"use strict";(self.webpackChunkexonumia_cc=self.webpackChunkexonumia_cc||[]).push([[65855],{27155:(a,e,n)=>{n.r(e),n.d(e,{data:()=>t});const t={key:"v-0d6cb31f",path:"/nga/ig/museum/re-bitcoin-v0.1-released/",title:"Re: Bitcoin v0.1 wepụtara",lang:"ig",frontmatter:{translators:[{name:"Joseph Stephen",href:"https://twitter.com/josephs20148614"}],supporters:[{name:"BitMEX",href:"https://blog.bitmex.com/bitmex-grant-translation-of-bitcoin-content-into-african-languages/"}]},excerpt:"",headers:[],filePathRelative:"nga/ig/museum/re-bitcoin-v0.1-released/README.md",git:{updatedTime:1761164621e3}}},60979:(a,e,n)=>{n.r(e),n.d(e,{default:()=>h});var t=n(66252);const o=(0,t._)("h1",{id:"re-bitcoin-v0-1-weputara",tabindex:"-1"},[(0,t._)("a",{class:"header-anchor",href:"#re-bitcoin-v0-1-weputara","aria-hidden":"true"},"#"),(0,t.Uk)(" Re: Bitcoin v0.1 wepụtara")],-1),r=(0,t.Uk)("nke Hal Finney "),i={href:"https://web.archive.org/web/20190712071421/https://www.mail-archive.com/cryptography@metzdowd.com/msg10152.html",target:"_blank",rel:"noopener noreferrer"},k=(0,t.Uk)("2009/01/11"),p=(0,t.uE)("<p>Satoshi Nakamoto ekwu, sị:</p><blockquote><p>Ịkpọsa mwepụta mbụ nke Bitcoin, ego eletrọnịkị ọhụrụ usoro na-eji netwọk ndị ọgbọ na ndị ọgbọ iji gbochie imefu okpukpu abụọ. Ọ bụ n&#39;ụzọ zuru ezu decentralized na-enweghị ihe nkesa ma ọ bụ Central ikike.</p><p>Hụ bitcoin.org maka nseta ihuenyo.</p><p>Budata njikọ: http://downloads.sourceforge.net/bitcoin/bitcoin-0.1.0.rar</p></blockquote><p>Ekele dịrị Satoshi na ntọhapụ alfa mbụ a. Ana m achọ na-atụ anya ịnwale ya.</p><blockquote><p>Mkpokọta nkesa ga-abụ mkpụrụ ego 21,000,000. A ga-ekesa ya na oghere netwọk mgbe ha na-eme ngọngọ, na-ebelata ego na ọkara kwa afọ 4 ọ bụla.</p><p>afọ 4 mbụ: mkpụrụ ego 10,500,000 afọ 4 sochirinụ: mkpụrụ ego 5,250,000 afọ 4 sochirinụ: mkpụrụ ego 2,625,000 afọ 4 sochirinụ: mkpụrụ ego 1,312,500 wdg...</p></blockquote><p>Ọ bụ ihe na-akpali na usoro nwere ike ahazi na-ekwe ka a ọnụ ọgụgụ kacha elu nke mkpụrụ ego a ga-emepụta. Echere m na echiche bụ na ego ole ọrụ achọrọ iji mepụta mkpụrụ ego ọhụrụ ga- na-esiwanye ike ka oge na-aga.</p><p>Otu nsogbu ozugbo na ego ọhụrụ ọ bụla bụ ka esi eji ya kpọrọ ihe. Ọbụna ileghara nsogbu bara uru nke ọ fọrọ nke nta ka ọ bụrụ na ọ dịghị onye ga-anabata ya na mbụ, a ka nwere ihe isi ike iji nweta ezi uche arụmụka na-akwado otu uru na-abụghị efu maka mkpụrụ ego ahụ.</p><p>Dị ka nnwale echiche na-atọ ụtọ, were ya na Bitcoin na-aga nke ọma na na-aghọ usoro ịkwụ ụgwọ kachasị na-eji n&#39;ụwa nile. Mgbe ahụ ngụkọta uru nke ego kwesịrị ịha nhata na mkpokọta uru niile akụ na ụba dị n&#39;ụwa. Atụmatụ ezinụlọ zuru ụwa ọnụ ugbu a akụ na ụba m chọtara sitere na $100 trillion ruo $300 trillion. Ya na 20 nde mkpụrụ ego, nke na-enye mkpụrụ ego nke ọ bụla uru ihe dị ka nde $10.</p><p>Ya mere, ohere nke ịmepụta mkpụrụ ego taa na cents ole na ole oge nwere ike ịbụ ezigbo nzọ, na-akwụ ụgwọ ihe dị ka 100 nde na 1! Ọbụlagodi na ohere nke Bitcoin ịga nke ọma n&#39;ọkwa a dị ntakịrị, ha bụ n&#39;ezie 100 nde otu megide? Ọ dị ihe ị ga-eche. ”…</p><p>Hal</p><hr><p>The Cryptography Mailing List Unsubscribe by sending &quot;unsubscribe cryptography&quot; to majord...@metzdowd.com</p>",11),g={},h=(0,n(83744).Z)(g,[["render",function(a,e){const n=(0,t.up)("OutboundLink"),g=(0,t.up)("LanguageDropdown");return(0,t.wg)(),(0,t.iD)(t.HY,null,[o,(0,t._)("p",null,[r,(0,t._)("a",i,[k,(0,t.Wm)(n)])]),(0,t.Wm)(g),p],64)}]])},83744:(a,e)=>{e.Z=(a,e)=>{const n=a.__vccOpts||a;for(const[a,t]of e)n[a]=t;return n}}}]);